WEBVTT

00:00.649 --> 00:01.756
The Passive Voice

00:02.682 --> 00:06.472
Sentences in the passive voice have their subjects receive the action.

00:08.611 --> 00:13.432
You can make the passive voice by using "was" plus a verb in the past tense.

00:15.314 --> 00:17.426
The music was played by the man.

00:20.090 --> 00:21.561
The cake was cut.

00:23.693 --> 00:26.103
The house was built in one day.

00:28.722 --> 00:30.932
The window was cleaned by the boy.

